item.title: New Massacre
item.dc:creator: @Xaro Xaro
item.description:
@Xaro wrote:

Mod Adam:

Tbh, I know I’ll get laughed at and shit on but, I lost 12m this way. A level 125 named (Boeds) had full dragon and a white phat on, he said he was going to teleport everyone to his house and the first to trade him would get his party hat. He did tele group, and I clicked accept without even reading, because I thought I was going to be the first one there and to get the phat. Turns out I was in Ice Plateau, got barraged, and watched his friend come down the line killing people 1 by one. I had to watch about 4 other people die until I was killed… Was pretty fun?

lmao i laughed at that story so hard. This is a good idea though. You would have to do this on one of the crowded worlds though.
